                    "{}{} was mutably borrowed here in the previous iteration of the loop{}",
                    desc,
                    via(opt_via),
                    opt_via,
                ),
            );
            if let Some(old_load_end_span) = old_load_end_span {
                err.span_label(old_load_end_span, "mutable borrow ends here");
            }
        } else {
